{"tid":1399180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一陣遊行終點係個大伏！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T05:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:30:41.000Z","uid":203818,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"58cb29f77d0953f5513a3271c3a136f3d87ef384","tid":1399180,"uid":203818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"遊行終點大概係櫻桃街公園嗰到，呢個地方好明顯係精心挑選過。<br />\n<br />\n一，櫻桃街公園距離各個地鐵站一段距離，正正位於旺角 奧運 油麻地 柯士甸站嘅中間，途步要行15分鐘，要逃離夢境都有啲困難。<br />\n<br />\n二，櫻桃街公園旁邊就係油麻地狗穴，內存大量瘋狗。<br />\n<br />\n三，大路基本上得幾條，班狗要做封鎖同包圍好容易，睇佢地都會係嗰條街狂放催淚彈。同埋班狗話會出水炮車，唔知會唔會今次出喇，地勢都好有利咁做。<br />\n<br />\n四，窄巷好多，狗好易拉一兩個入暗角去私刑。<br />\n<br />\n歸納，十分有利班狗做拒捕。"},{"pid":"27a3841e68c95b07d0fe8085e90df73caf0042da","tid":1399180,"uid":203818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6a396cfb1e4c6d51467bd30275f1b7bbcd8ce225","tid":1399180,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c38ef4c7e53acfe426c4c8c4ec7704525ed35222","tid":1399180,"uid":203818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"468ed1b57a788900bf0261b099441c5239595205","tid":1399180,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1d9363e9da74ea4142023fc7856fabdf6008e99","tid":1399180,"uid":63912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3070c6ad34b5b44a91f6afb8aba1aee5d0e49336","tid":1399180,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"行少少就好走快閃啦<br />\n仲終點"},{"pid":"6960d01d7da7496778264d505f934f6404ac578d","tid":1399180,"uid":221819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"轉場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eea7dd7ac7efe9865a3128b57c08b541327e83f","tid":13